General.Name: Metal Gayrimenkul Anonim Sirketi
General.Description: Metal Gayrimenkul Anonim Sirketi engages in the portfolio management business. The company was formerly known as Metro Altin Isletmeciligi Insaat Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Metal Gayrimenkul Anonim Sirketi in November 2013. Metal Gayrimenkul Anonim Sirketi was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
